view.welcome: Nau mai ki ARC!  Hangaia ngā ataata whaiaro ki tētahi o ā mātou holograms me te whakairi ki ō hongere pāpāho pāpori!
view.text-step-1: Kōwhiria he hologram mai i te puna.
view.text-step-2: He Ao Rangirua tēnei, nā reira ka karapatia te mokowā ki tō kāmera mai i te taha ki te taha mō te 3-5 hēkona e hiahia ana koe kia noho te mahinga hologram.
view.text-step-3-part-1: Kia kotahi te mata i te tauwāhi e hiahia ana koe kia punga te hologram.
view.text-step-3-part-2: AKI!  Kia kotahi te pato ki tētahi atu wāhi hei nuku i te hologram ki tētahi atu tūnga.
view.text-step-3-part-3: AKI!  Ka taea e koe te whakarahi anō i te hologram mā te kini, mā te whakawhānui rānei i te mata ki tō kōnui me tō matimati taupū.
view.text-step-4-part-1: Pato tauruatia te pātene pūkete whero hei START i tō hopukanga ataata.
view.text-step-4-part-2: Pato tauruatia te pātene pūkete whero ki STOP.
